<div class="container" style="padding-top: 100px;">
    <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 60px;">
        <h1 class="animate-title" style="font-size: 3.5rem; color: var(--primary);">
            <%= t('join_family') %>
        </h1>
        <p class="animate-subtitle" style="font-size: 1.2rem; max-width: 700px; margin: 20px auto; line-height: 1.8;">
            Activities are open and accessible.<br>
            You decide the value at the end.<br>
            <strong>Like a Free Tour, but for community.</strong>
        </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Simple How It Works -->
    <div
        style="background: var(--naif-mint); padding: 50px; border-radius: 40px; margin-bottom: 60px; text-align: center;">
        <h3 style="margin-bottom: 30px;">How it works</h3>
        <div class="grid" style="grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 30px;">
            <div>
                <div style="font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 15px;">üìÖ</div>
                <h4>1. Pick an activity</h4>
                <p style="font-size: 0.95rem; opacity: 0.8;">Browse the calendar and reserve your spot</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <div style="font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 15px;">ü§ù</div>
                <h4>2. Show up & connect</h4>
                <p style="font-size: 0.95rem; opacity: 0.8;">Meet the community and enjoy the experience</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <div style="font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 15px;">üíõ</div>
                <h4>3. Contribute by will</h4>
                <p style="font-size: 0.95rem; opacity: 0.8;">Pay what feels right at the end</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ Section -->
    <div style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <h2 style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 40px;">Quick Questions</h2>

        <div class="card" style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 30px;">
            <h4 style="color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 10px;">Do I need to pay upfront?</h4>
            <p>No. All activities are free to join. At the end, you contribute what you think is fair.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card" style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 30px;">
            <h4 style="color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 10px;">Can I come alone?</h4>
            <p>Absolutely! Most people come solo. That's the whole point‚Äîmaking new friends.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card" style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 30px;">
            <h4 style="color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 10px;">What if I can't make it?</h4>
            <p>Just let us know via WhatsApp. No penalties, no stress.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card" style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 30px;">
            <h4 style="color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 10px;">How do I stay updated?</h4>
            <p>Join our WhatsApp group or follow us on Instagram for announcements and last-minute plans.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Social CTAs -->
    <div
        style="text-align: center; margin-top: 60px; padding: 50px; background: var(--naif-yellow); border-radius: 40px;">
        <h3 style="margin-bottom: 30px;">Stay Connected</h3>
        <div style="display: flex; gap: 20px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;">
            <a href="https://wa.me/YOUR_WHATSAPP_NUMBER" target="_blank" class="btn"
                style="background: #25D366; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;">
                <span style="font-size: 1.5rem;">üí¨</span> WhatsApp Group
            </a>
            <a href="https://instagram.com/murciawelcomesyou" target="_blank" class="btn"
                style="background: #E4405F; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;">
                <span style="font-size: 1.5rem;">üì∏</span> Instagram
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/3.12.5/gsap.min.js"></script>
<script>
    gsap.from(".animate-title", { opacity: 0, y: -30, duration: 1, ease: "power2.out" });
    gsap.from(".animate-subtitle", { opacity: 0, y: -20, delay: 0.2, duration: 1 });
</script>